&lt;p&gt;Service bean that should be autowired in &lt;code&gt;MileageFeeCalculator&lt;/code&gt; but it isn&apos;t:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-java s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-meta&quot;&gt;@Service&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-keyword&quot;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title class_&quot;&gt;MileageRateService&lt;/span&gt; {
